* add a stub for VDI.resize

0.9.3 (6-Jul-2013):
* SR.stat now works (so size reporting via xapi works)

0.9.2 (30-Jun-2013):
* libvirt ceph storage now works

0.9.1 (30-Jun-2013):
* now takes entire libvirt storage pool XML fragments in SR attach, create
* SR.attach is now idempotent
* version 0.9.7 of the storage API test passes

0.9.0 (31-May-2013):
* first public release

